divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting on the porch watching the bats fly around. I saw an orange colored orb moving from north to south at a very high rate of speed. It was completely silent and had no trail behind it like a meteorite.it took the object all of two seconds to move from the roofline to behind the trees which is about fifteen degrees.
Summary: i saw a bright orange orb very quickly moving south
